  Order to Write It

  1. Indexing — you know this best, write it first
  2. Ranking — explain each model with formulas
  3. Evaluation — complete pool.csv judgements first, then write with actual numbers
  4. Introduction + Abstract — write these last when you know the full picture
  5. Conclusions — reflect honestly on limitations
